    <fr:title text="Forester 5.0 [TBA] › new datalog-based query engine › renamed built-in relations"><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-013A.xml" title="Forester 5.0 [TBA] › new datalog-based query engine" addr="forest://forester/jms-013A" type="local"><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-011P.xml" title="Forester 5.0 [TBA]" addr="forest://forester/jms-011P" type="local">Forester 5.0 [TBA]</fr:link> › new datalog-based query engine</fr:link> › renamed built-in relations</fr:title>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Forester’s built-in binary relations have been accessible via macros like <html:code><![CDATA[\rel/authors]]></html:code>, etc. In this release, these relations are being renamed to make them more pleasant and consistent to use with datalog.</html:p>
